  "instructions": [
    "Heat the raclette grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Cook the ground beef in the raclette grill until browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the raclette grill and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the crushed tomatoes, beef broth, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper to the raclette grill. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and let cook for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the kidney beans and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Season the bean mixture with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Transfer the bean mixture to a baking dish and top with feta cheese.",
    "Bake for 15 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Serve the bean mixture in the ssam wraps with crushed taco shells on top."
